{
  "stem": "12868.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 367.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it happened someday I pushed by myself into-- go into work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I bringing something to-- to trade for a piece of bread, for a piece of butter, a piece-- something flour, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I wrap up everywhere I can.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I then go through-- to the-- to the-- to the gate, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this what I keep up my parents, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With everything little by little, we got-- we got to manage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How I know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never-- I didn't want to know them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans-- I never see Germans in my life in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The German army.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German army, the SS.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The SS, they stay by the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They stay by the tower.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they let you out, and they let you in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they search you every day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But sometimes, it was, in the ghetto, Yiddish police, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the Jew-- the Yiddish police take care inside in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they have to wear like-- like all of we got to wear, the star.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The yellow star got to wear-- even a-- a baby from three months, even, you got to wear a star.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure I know them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of the Jewish police, we make with them-- we make with them-- he give something to the German police, you know, like a-- like a ring, something somebody had.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or somebody had a little vase or something like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the morning, let him back through.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let him through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let him through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let him through.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was uniforms with a Yiddish-- with a Jewish star, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With a helmet with a Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A uniform they had.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What the-- the Germans make him to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
